data.description: Cute as a button and ready for a new owner!  This well-maintained home has 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, an open kitchen/dining area, a large living area with a wood-burning fireplace, a large backyard for entertaining, and it is just a few steps from Penick Park!  There have been several updates to the home over the last couple of years:  new roof in Jan 2020, new appliances, granite counter tops in the bathrooms, tankless water heater, new retaining wall, new privacy fence, and new flooring just to name a few.  This one is just waiting for you to come make it yours.  Schedule an appointment today!
